The user should be able to click a button on the home page that starts the quiz
Users should be prompted through a series of at least 5 multiple choice questions that they can answer.
    Users should be asked questions 1 after the other.
    Users should only be prompted with 1 question at a time.
Users are required to answer each question.
Users should be able to see what question they are on.
Users should be able to see how many questions they have answered correctly out of the total.
Users should be provided feedback with the correct answer, if they answered incorrectly.
after recieving feedback the user should either be moved onto the next question or prompted to move on.
At the end of the quiz, users should be provided with their score. How many they answered correctly out of the total.
At the end of the quiz, users should be able to start the quiz over.
